      <guid isPermaLink="false">Google-I/O-前夕，Gemini-3.2-Flash-与多款「Agent」模型提前曝光</guid>
      <description>&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 80%; letter-spacing: .001rem; font-size: .875rem;line-height: 1.375rem; margin-bottom: 5%;line-height: 1.375rem&quot;&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://s3.ifanr.com/images/ep/uploads/lark2pad_upload/7d0a9bc1-0220-453d-9403-b02ce57547e7.jpg&quot;/&gt;
